# {{ project_name }}

## Build

./gradlew assemble

## Verify (all must pass before committing)

./gradlew ktlintCheck
./gradlew test

## Git

Always work on a feature branch. Never commit directly to main.
Branch prefixes: feature/, fix/, refactor/, docs/

## Rules

- Run verify after every code change, before committing
- Never edit generated files in pragma-core/build/ directly
- Pragma plugins implement interfaces in pragma-plugin-common; check extension points before adding new ones
- Run `./gradlew ktlintFormat` to auto-fix style issues before committing
